D nekkni i d taftilt n tmurt i d-iceɛlen.
Ad d-nesban idles-nneɣ anda t-ffren.
Ad t-nnadi, ad nesteqsi, ad nruḥ tuddar lexla
Ayen ara nwali, ad aɣ-d-yawi si yal d tamusni swayes ara tebnu tmurt uzekka.
Adrar s adrar slan, wa yessawal-as gma-s seg wa ɣer wa.
Yewweḍ-d lexbar yelhan yezzi-asent am uzrar akk i tmura.
Mi ara ddukklen ad akk sefḍen akk imeṭṭi n wass-a.
Freḥ yis-sen, tedεuḍ-asen ad ssiwḍen.
I wakken yis-sen ara icennu uzekka.
Yuli-d yiṭij yecreq, yesban-aɣ-d akk iberdan s anda ara neffeɣ.
Agdud yellan yefreq, yeddukel-d afus deg ufus yedda-d yid-neɣ.
Ahaw akit akken ad d-nawit ṣṣut-nwen ɣur-neɣ.
Wa s tcelḥit, wa s temêabit, wa s tcawit i wakken ad d-tekker tmaziɣt-nneɣ.
